import useFetch from '../services/UserService'
import { useParams } from 'react-router'

function RadialBarChart(data) {
    const { userId } = useParams()
    const { userData, isLoaded } = useFetch(userId.slice(-2))

    return (
        <>
            <svg
                className="score-box rounded bg-gray-50"
                width="250"
                height="250"
            >
                <circle cx="125" cy="125" r="87" fill="white"></circle>
                <text x="32" y="35" fill="#20253A" fontSize="15">
                    Score
                </text>
                <text
                    x="109"
                    y="100"
                    fill="#20253A"
                    fontSize="19"
                    fontWeight="bold"
                >
                    {isLoaded && userData.score * 100}%
                </text>
                <text
                    x="102"
                    y="130"
                    fill="#20253A"
                    fontSize="16"
                    className="opacity-50"
                >
                    de votre
                </text>
                <text
                    x="105"
                    y="160"
                    fill="#20253A"
                    fontSize="16"
                    className="opacity-50"
                >
                    objectif
                </text>
            </svg>
        </>
    )
}

export default RadialBarChart
